Important addresses

Sheraton Four Points: 1900 E. Speedway Boulevard, Tucson AZ 85719. Tel: (520) 327-7341.

Sahara Apartments: 919 N. Stone Avenue, Tucson AZ 85705. Tel: (520) 622-4102.

Lectures: Talks will take place in Room 202 of the Aerospace and Mechanical Engineering (AME) building on the University of Arizona campus. For the purpose of online mapping websites you may use the address 1130 N. Mountain Ave., Tucson AZ 85721. AME is on the northeast corner of Speedway and Mountain, several blocks west of the Sheraton. The best entrance to the lecture hall is through the courtyard separating the two wings of the AME building.
